cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.CL 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a method based on deep reinforcement learning. It also involves the use of knowledge graphs, which suggests it could be relevant to cs.DB (Databases) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper aims to provide good explanations, which could be related to the sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
